title: Jessica Mauboy on campaign for Aussie Eurovision glory
text:
Jessica Mauboy on campaign for Aussie Eurovision glory 8:01pm IST - 02:07 
Indigenous Australian popstar Jessica Mauboy has a London performance of her song ‘We Got Love’ on the campaign trail for Aussie Eurovision glory. Jayson Mansaray reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
